articles.title: What is COVAX-19, the most advanced of Australia's remaining local COVID vaccine candidates? - Medical Xpress
articles.description: Australia's current crop of COVID-19 vaccines consists of a shot by American biotechnology company Pfizer, which we import, and the vaccine by British-Swedish multinational AstraZeneca, the bulk of which we manufacture onshore in Melbourne under license.
